<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AI Agent Memory Toolkit — Production-Ready Memory Architecture | ZOO</title>
<meta name="description" content="Production-ready memory architecture for AI agents. Vector store, hierarchical memory, multi-agent sharing. Python + ChromaDB. $39 one-time.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,400;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--bg:#0a0a0b;--surface:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);--surface2:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);--border:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);--border-h:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);--text:#e4e4e7;--text2:#8888a0;--text3:#55556a;--accent:#a855f7;--accent2:#c084fc;--accent-glow:rgba(168,85,247,0.15);--accent-glow2:rgba(168,85,247,0.25);--green:#22c55e;--pink:#ec4899;--cyan:#06b6d4;--font-serif:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;--font-sans:'Inter',-apple-system,sans-serif;--ease:cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1)}
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;background:var(--bg);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
body{font-family:var(--font-sans);background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden}
::selection{background:var(--accent);color:#fff}
.noise{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:9999;pointer-events:none;opacity:0.018;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 512 512' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='.85' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");background-size:512px}
.nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:1000;padding:20px 48px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;background:rgba(10,10,11,0.85);backdrop-filter:blur(30px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:all 0.6s var(--ease)}
.nav.scrolled{padding:14px 48px;background:rgba(10,10,11,0.95)}
.nav-logo{font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.02em}
.nav-logo em{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff6b35,#ff8a5c,#ec4899);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;font-style:normal}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;list-style:none;align-items:center}
.nav-links a{color:var(--text2);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:500;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.14em;transition:color 0.3s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--text)}
.nav-cta{padding:10px 24px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff6b35,#ff8a5c);color:#fff;font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-decoration:none;border-radius:8px;transition:all 0.4s var(--ease)}
.nav-cta:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(255,107,53,0.3)}
.hero{position:relative;padding:160px 48px 80px;overflow:hidden}
.hero-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:0}
.hero-bg::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-30%;right:-20%;width:700px;height:700px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(168,85,247,0.06) 0%,transparent 70%);border-radius:50%}
.hero-grid{position:relative;z-index:2;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:60px;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;align-items:center}
.hero-left{max-width:560px}
.hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:6px 16px;background:rgba(168,85,247,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(168,85,247,0.2);border-radius:100px;font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:24px}
.hero-badge::before{content:'';width:6px;height:6px;background:var(--accent);border-radius:50%;animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0.4}}
.hero-title{font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4vw,3.4rem);font-weight:900;line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:20px}
.hero-title .gradient{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--pink),var(--cyan));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}
.hero-desc{color:var(--text2);font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:32px}
.hero-ctas{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:16px 32px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.4s var(--ease);border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--font-sans)}
.btn-primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));color:#fff;box-shadow:0 4px 24px var(--accent-glow)}
.btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 12px 40px var(--accent-glow2)}
.btn-secondary{background:var(--surface2);color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--border)}
.btn-secondary:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.hero-price{margin-top:28px;display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px}
.hero-price .amount{font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--text)}
.hero-price .period{color:var(--text3);font-size:0.85rem}
.hero-visual{position:relative;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.hero-visual-inner{width:100%;max-width:440px;aspect-ratio:1;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(168,85,247,0.06),rgba(236,72,153,0.03));border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:40px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero-visual-inner::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%,rgba(168,85,247,0.08),transparent 60%)}
.viz-icon{font-size:5rem;margin-bottom:20px;position:relative;z-index:2;filter:drop-shadow(0 8px 30px rgba(168,85,247,0.3))}
.viz-label{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text2);position:relative;z-index:2;font-weight:500}
.viz-modules{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:20px;position:relative;z-index:2;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center}
.viz-mod{padding:4px 12px;background:rgba(168,85,247,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(168,85,247,0.15);border-radius:20px;font-size:0.65rem;color:var(--accent);font-weight:600}
.section{padding:100px 48px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.section-inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto}
.section-eyebrow{font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:16px;text-align:center}
.section-title{font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.6rem);font-weight:800;text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px;letter-spacing:-0.02em}
.section-subtitle{color:var(--text2);font-size:1.05rem;text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 60px;line-height:1.7}
.arch-diagram{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px;margin-bottom:60px}
.arch-layer{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:32px;text-align:center;transition:all 0.4s var(--ease)}
.arch-layer:hover{border-color:rgba(168,85,247,0.2);transform:translateY(-4px)}
.arch-layer-num{font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:900;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.5}
.arch-layer h3{font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}
.arch-layer p{color:var(--text2);font-size:0.84rem;line-height:1.6}
.features-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:20px}
.feature-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:32px;transition:all 0.4s var(--ease)}
.feature-card:hover{border-color:rgba(168,85,247,0.2);transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)}
.feature-icon{font-size:1.8rem;margin-bottom:14px}
.feature-card h3{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px}
.feature-card p{color:var(--text2);font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.65}
.buy-section{padding:120px 48px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.buy-section::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:700px;height:700px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(168,85,247,0.06) 0%,rgba(236,72,153,0.03) 35%,transparent 70%);border-radius:50%}
.buy-card{position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:24px;padding:60px 48px}
.buy-card:hover{border-color:rgba(168,85,247,0.2)}
.buy-badge{display:inline-block;padding:4px 14px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--pink));color:#fff;border-radius:20px;font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:20px}
.buy-title{font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.4rem);font-weight:800;margin-bottom:12px;letter-spacing:-0.02em}
.buy-desc{color:var(--text2);font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:32px;line-height:1.7}
.buy-price{font-size:3rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px}
.buy-price .currency{font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700}
.buy-period{color:var(--text3);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:32px}
.buy-features{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:36px}
.buy-feature{padding:6px 16px;background:rgba(168,85,247,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(168,85,247,0.1);border-radius:8px;font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text2)}
.buy-guarantee{margin-top:24px;color:var(--text3);font-size:0.78rem}
.buy-guarantee a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none}
.why-section{padding:80px 48px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.why-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:20px}
.why-item{padding:28px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;text-align:center}
.why-item-icon{font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:12px}
.why-item h3{font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}
.why-item p{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.6}
.footer{padding:48px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);text-align:center}
.footer p{color:var(--text3);font-size:0.78rem}
.footer a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none}
.footer-links{display:flex;gap:24px;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.footer-links a{color:var(--text2);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.78rem;transition:color 0.3s}
.footer-links a:hover{color:var(--text)}
.fade-up{opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.8s var(--ease),transform 0.8s var(--ease)}
.fade-up.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
@media(max-width:900px){.hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px}.hero-visual{order:-1}.arch-diagram{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
@media(max-width:768px){.nav{padding:16px 20px}.nav-links{display:none}.hero{padding:130px 20px 60px}.section,.buy-section,.why-section{padding:70px 20px}.buy-card{padding:40px 24px}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="noise"></div>
<nav class="nav" id="nav">
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">ZOO<em>.</em></a>
  <ul class="nav-links"><li><a href="/">Home</a></li><li><a href="/products">Products</a></li><li><a href="/pricing.html">Pricing</a></li><li><a href="/blog.html">Blog</a></li></ul>
  <a href="#buy" class="nav-cta">Get the Toolkit — $39</a>
</nav>
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="hero-badge">AI Memory Architecture</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Give your AI agents <span class="gradient">perfect memory.</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">Production-ready memory architecture for AI agents. Vector store, hierarchical memory, memory consolidation, multi-agent sharing. Python + ChromaDB. Self-hosted.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas"><a href="#buy" class="btn btn-primary">Get the Toolkit — $39 →</a><a href="#architecture" class="btn btn-secondary">See Architecture</a></div>
      <div class="hero-price"><span class="amount">$39</span><span class="period">one-time payment</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="hero-visual-inner">
        <div class="viz-icon">🧠</div>
        <div class="viz-label">AI Agent Memory Toolkit</div>
        <div class="viz-modules"><span class="viz-mod">Vector Store</span><span class="viz-mod">Hierarchical</span><span class="viz-mod">Consolidation</span><span class="viz-mod">Multi-Agent</span><span class="viz-mod">Production</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="section" id="architecture">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Architecture</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three layers of <span style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--pink));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent">intelligent memory.</span></h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Inspired by how human memory works — but optimized for AI agents that need to recall, consolidate, and share knowledge.</p>
    <div class="arch-diagram">
      <div class="arch-layer fade-up"><div class="arch-layer-num">1</div><h3>Working Memory</h3><p>Fast, short-term context for the current conversation. Auto-expires. Keeps the agent focused.</p></div>
      <div class="arch-layer fade-up"><div class="arch-layer-num">2</div><h3>Episodic Memory</h3><p>Vector-stored conversation history. Semantic search. The agent remembers what happened and when.</p></div>
      <div class="arch-layer fade-up"><div class="arch-layer-num">3</div><h3>Semantic Memory</h3><p>Consolidated knowledge graph. Distilled insights. Grows smarter over time automatically.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card fade-up"><div class="feature-icon">🔍</div><h3>Vector Memory Store</h3><p>ChromaDB-powered semantic search. Store and retrieve any type of knowledge with sub-second latency.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-card fade-up"><div class="feature-icon">🏗️</div><h3>Hierarchical Memory</h3><p>Three-tier architecture: working, episodic, semantic. Each layer optimized for its purpose.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-card fade-up"><div class="feature-icon">🧹</div><h3>Memory Consolidation</h3><p>Automatic distillation of raw conversations into structured knowledge. Gets smarter over time.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-card fade-up"><div class="feature-icon">🤝</div><h3>Multi-Agent Sharing</h3><p>Redis-backed shared memory pool. Multiple agents can read/write to a common knowledge base.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-card fade-up"><div class="feature-icon">🐍</div><h3>Production Agent Class</h3><p>Drop-in Agent class with memory built in. Works with LangChain, LangGraph, or standalone.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-card fade-up"><div class="feature-icon">📊</div><h3>Memory Analytics</h3><p>Track memory usage, hit rates, and quality metrics. Know when consolidation is needed.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="buy-section" id="buy">
  <div class="buy-card">
    <div class="buy-badge">New Release</div>
    <h2 class="buy-title">Get the Complete Toolkit</h2>
    <p class="buy-desc">3-layer memory architecture. Python + ChromaDB + Redis. Lifetime updates. Self-hosted.</p>
    <div class="buy-price"><span class="currency">$</span>39</div>
    <div class="buy-period">one-time payment · instant delivery</div>
    <div class="buy-features">
      <span class="buy-feature">✅ Vector Memory Store</span><span class="buy-feature">✅ Hierarchical Memory</span><span class="buy-feature">✅ Memory Consolidation</span><span class="buy-feature">✅ Multi-Agent Sharing</span><span class="buy-feature">✅ Production Agent Class</span><span class="buy-feature">✅ Memory Analytics</span><span class="buy-feature">✅ Lifetime Updates</span><span class="buy-feature">✅ Email Support</span>
    </div>
    <a href="/checkout.html?product=memory-toolkit&price=39" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size:1.05rem;padding:18px 40px">Get the Toolkit → $39</a>
    <div class="buy-guarantee">🔒 Secured by Stripe · 30-day money-back guarantee · <a href="/">ZOO Technologies</a></div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="why-section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Why ZOO</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Built by an AI-native company that ships.</h2>
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-item"><div class="why-item-icon">⚡</div><h3>Ship in Hours</h3><p>Production-ready code. Not a toy. Real patterns you can deploy today.</p></div>
      <div class="why-item"><div class="why-item-icon">🔄</div><h3>Lifetime Updates</h3><p>Buy once, get every future update free. We improve constantly.</p></div>
      <div class="why-item"><div class="why-item-icon">🛡️</div><h3>30-Day Guarantee</h3><p>Not satisfied? Full refund. No questions. No risk.</p></div>
      <div class="why-item"><div class="why-item-icon">💬</div><h3>Email Support</h3><p>Stuck? We respond within 24 hours. Real help.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-links"><a href="/">Home</a><a href="/products">Products</a><a href="/pricing.html">Pricing</a><a href="/blog.html">Blog</a></div>
  <p>© 2026 <a href="/">ZOO Technologies</a> · AI-Powered Technology Studio · All payments secured by Stripe</p>
</footer>
<script>
const nav=document.getElementById('nav');
window.addEventListener('scroll',()=>{nav.classList.toggle('scrolled',window.scrollY>60)});
const observer=new IntersectionObserver((entries)=>{entries.forEach(e=>{if(e.isIntersecting)e.target.classList.add('visible')})},{threshold:0.1,rootMargin:'0px 0px -50px 0px'});
document.querySelectorAll('.fade-up').forEach(el=>observer.observe(el));
</script>
</body>
</html>
